      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/171/5739",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلْمَمْلُوكِ وَ اَلْمَمْلُوكَةِ هَلْ يَحْجُبَانِ إِذَا لَمْ يَرِثَا قَالَ \"لاَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5739 - Ali ibn Mahziyar narrated from Fadalah from Aban from Al-Fadl ibn Abd Al-Malik who said: I asked Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a male and female slave - do they prevent others from inheriting if they themselves do not inherit?\nImam (as) replied: \"No.\""
        ]
      }
    },
